Description:
Objective:
To Test Credit Card Service Order with two different Gateways (PUBLIC AND GLOBAL)

Pre-requisites:

"Credit Card Payment Gateway related setup should be done in the test company for all three Payment Gateways - FreedomPay, GlobalOnePay and JDF.
In the 'Payment Gateway Details' (xiext6100m000) session, Business Parameter field should contain B. P. code."

Steps_Service Credit Card Invoicing :

"Book a Service Order with Mode of Payment - 'Credit Card'.
Add Parts/Labor/Others lines.
Release the Service Order.
Book Actual Cost.
Cost and Invoice the Order.
Enter Credit Card details for GlobalOnePay card 5100270000000007 and CVV 214.
Click 'Process' in the Credit Card Interface session."

Expected Result:
Two invoices should get generated in the 'Open Entries' (tfacr2520m000) session - One against Order B.P. and one against Payment Gateway B.P. maintained in the 'Payment Gateway Details' (xiext6100m000) session. Invoice Balance for Invoice against Order B.P. should be $0.
Service Order>Header Invoice Details ie read invoice series and amount
Service Order>Check open entries for CC BP and Invoice BP
